Text: Catch Me (TVXQ song):  Written by Yoo Young-jin and Yoo Han-jin, two versions of "Catch Me" exist: the original Korean-language version, which served as the lead single for the duo's sixth Korean studio album "Catch Me" (2012), and a Japanese-language version, which was released as the fourth and last single for their sixth Japanese studio album, "Time" (2013).
